725195f-a.title: Queens: 31st Avenue - 50th Street
725195f-a.text:
31st Avenue, north side, at 50th Street, showing Public
School No. 151. The view is north froa Broadway and on the
right (telephone poles) is the Old Bowery Bay Road, now 51st
Street.
P. L. Sperr  June 23, 1932
